definition.value: 2-hydroxy-3-oxopropanoate + H(+) + [NADH or NADPH] => D-glycerate + [NAD(+) or NADP(+)].
1 2-oxoglutarate + 1 H(+) + 1 L-lysine + 1 NADPH => 1 H(2)O + 1 NADP(+) + 1 saccharopine.
1 H(2)O + 1 NAD(+) + 1 saccharopine => 1 H(+) + 1 L-2-aminoadipate 6-semialdahyde + 1 L-glutamate + 1 NADH.
H(2)O + L-2-aminoadipate 6-semialdahyde + [NAD(+) or NADP(+)] => H(+) + L-alpha-aminoadipate + [NADH or NADPH].
1 H(+) + 1 NADPH + 1 O(2) + 1 indole => 1 H(2)O + 1 NADP(+) + 1 indolin-2-one.
1 H(+) + 1 NADPH + 1 O(2) + 1 indolin-2-one => 1 3-hydroxyindolin-2-one + 1 H(2)O + 1 NADP(+).
H(2)O + benzaldehyde + [NAD(+) or NADP(+)] => H(+) + benzoate + [NADH or NADPH].
H(+) + dihydrobiopterin + [NADH or NADPH] => tetrahydrobiopterin + [NAD(+) or NADP(+)].
1 H(2)O + 1 L-leucine + 1 NAD(+) => 1 4-methyl-2-oxopentanoate + 1 H(+) + 1 NADH + 1 NH(3).
1 H(2)O + 1 amicyanin + 1 methylamine => 2 H(+) + 1 NH(3) + 1 formaldehyde + 1 reduced amicyanin.
